The Assemblyman's Office was more helpful to several Constituents in the neighborhood.
.
His staff was thorough, professional and very courteous, with varied language skills which is a plus.The Assembly Member, himself, is quite empathic and listens carefully to each and every concern or suggestion when an appointment is made to see him. Too, having Open House hours is great.
.
A very positive overall experience.
